  "description": "<p>Let the little explorers enjoy the luxurious comfort of their own down bag. The Draco line delivers all the benefits of a technical down bag at a price you'd expect to pay for synthetic. Tightly woven shell fabric, baffles in the torso region and drawcords contain warmth. Tapered cut allows a little bit of movement while they sleep off the night\u2019s s'more feast.</p><ul><li>Pertex\u00ae Quantum ripstop nylon shell has a DWR treatment to shed moisture and a tight weave to retain down</li><li>30-denier woven nylon lining</li><li>Insulated with 650 fill power duck down that meets the Responsible Down Standard for animal welfare</li><li>Vertical baffles over the torso prevent cold spots</li><li>Rear Pad Lock secures the sleeping bag to the sleeping mat</li><li>Medium-width cut</li><li>Hood and shoulder drawcords have different profiles, so you can tell them apart in the dark. Small size\u2019s hood is externally adjustable with a hook-and-loops strap, making it easy to snug-up when you are tucking in the littlest campers</li><li>Draft tube keeps heat in and cold out</li><li>Drawcord stuff sack and large storage sack included</li><li>EN standard tested, for dependable temperature ratings</li></ul>",
